description1.name: Description
description1.value: This beautifully renovated 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-storey family home exudes both comfort and elegance. The bright, modern kitchen includes a large island perfect  for entertaining, featuring premium finishes, seamlessly flows into the sunken family room with a welcoming fireplace. The main floor also boasts an inviting formal dining room, a spacious living room, and a stylish bathroom, along with a newly updated laundry room with convenient access to the garage. Upstairs, you'll discover 4 generously proportioned bedrooms, including a luxurious primary suite with a spacious walk-in closet and a gorgeous ensuite bathroom.  The additional 5-piece bathroom is equally sophisticated, designed with meticulous attention to detail, enhanced by heated floors and high-end fixtures for ultimate comfort. Outside, the home features a fully fenced backyard retreat, complete with a large deck, gazebo, and an above-ground pool, providing the perfect space for relaxation on warm summer days.  The spacious basement is waiting for your final touches to finish it the way you would like it. This homes incredible curb appeal is further enhanced by all-new concrete at the front entrance, side of the home, and a newly updated driveway leading to a double car garage. Ideally located near top-tier schools, shops, restaurants, local wineries and orchards truly giving you  sense of escape from busy city life in a family friendly neighbourhood.  Easy access to highways and a short distance from Lake Ontario, Toronto and Niagara Falls. This home has it all combing modern luxury with convenience! Fall in love with the perfect property in a lovely community. Note: New information stated that a GO Station is proposed in Beamsville across from Sobeys (9 minute walk from the property).

summary.name: Summary
value: The house has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms.
It is a 2-storey family home with a bright, modern kitchen and a sunken family room.
The main floor includes a formal dining room, a living room, a bathroom, and a laundry room.
Upstairs, there are 4 bedrooms, including a primary suite with a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom.
The home features a fully fenced backyard with a large deck, gazebo, and an above-ground pool.
The basement is spacious and waiting for final touches.
The house is located near top-tier schools, shops, restaurants, and has easy access to highways and Lake Ontario.
